{"tid":697090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺旺角俾人截停嘅朋友小心","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:10.000Z","uid":132246,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44695dfefdbe365751282915953e2e503b6be6f4","tid":697090,"uid":132246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:14:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱行過旺角潮特街口趕巴士，有個肥婆走過嚟話自己唔見咗銀包有無錢借，同時間好大力咁捉住我左手。<br />\n<br />\n我梗係無現佢直行直過，但係佢啲指甲勁長，一嘢就刮落隻手度。上咗車先見到有傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落車真係要去消毒先<br />\n<br />\n大家行街真係要小心啲，尤其無啦啦嘅身體接觸<br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/001348_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F001348_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eadce59d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70cb7e3240a424a1299f4b0d1efb3dbada81bf9e","tid":697090,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾 俾肥婆捉住都唔敢還拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲敢po上嚟"},{"pid":"62bd1462aedd7c84459f34ba683343ea8847847a","tid":697090,"uid":132246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70cb7e3240a424a1299f4b0d1efb3dbada81bf9e","tid":697090,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾 俾肥婆捉住都唔敢還拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲敢po上嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"諗住係普通騙子，無視佢就算"},{"pid":"a